{"tid":2245322,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"堵路現場私了持磚頭內地漢 三人今認罪 10月28日判刑","createTime":"2020-10-16T06:37:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-28T09:30:35.000Z","uid":240362,"like":4,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"eb0073bb0d8059bcc4afca8dacf1b31e106e7b8c","tid":2245322,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T06:37:36.000Z","msg":"去年10月5日蒙面法正式生效，有市民在旺角聚集抗議，當晚現場有內地遊客及本地男子分別因 「影人相」及移走堵路雜物，被人誤以為是警員，遭毆打「私了」。警方事後拘控一對本地男女及一名埃及籍男子，三人今在區域法院認罪，還柙候判。其中年近六旬的清潔工被告稱當晚為保護青年示威者，帶備金屬棒到場，及後發現涉案內地遊客手執磚頭，他遂大叫：「你做乜拎磚頭？放低！」並且捧打對方，因而犯案。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201016/D6AV462PEVFQXF65S6STXORHYQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201016%2FD6AV462PEVFQXF65S6STXORHYQ%2F&d=Z58AETknIeTPCCdXMCOVU6EbpHCTTcQcXY6VsQHNTK4%3D&h=4cb3146a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201016%2FD6AV462PEVFQXF65S6STXORHYQ%2F&h=d134b564\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201016/D6AV462PEVFQXF65S6STXORHYQ/</a>"},{"pid":"275497f3af5bb44baebdbea6fef1307e4572d3fb","tid":2245322,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T06:47:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b98dabe1548c97a841a59beb772a57b8e107434","tid":2245322,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"275497f3af5bb44baebdbea6fef1307e4572d3fb","tid":2245322,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T06:47:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T06:49:53.000Z","msg":"<i